1
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,680
My wedding with Ms. Xia Wanqing

2
00:00:15,281 --> 00:00:16,241
will be kept simple,

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,281
mainly for important clients.

4
00:00:18,561 --> 00:00:19,520
Any questions?

5
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,121
No objections here.

6
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:24,000
As for the company and the wedding,

7
00:00:24,081 --> 00:00:25,320
we'll follow Mr. Gu's lead.

8
00:00:27,081 --> 00:00:27,640
Good.

9
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:31,200
Now, another announcement:

10
00:00:31,721 --> 00:00:33,960
Ji Xiaoxue will be my personal assistant.

11
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:35,641
From now on,

12
00:00:36,041 --> 00:00:37,081
her opinion is my opinion.

13
00:00:56,681 --> 00:00:57,920
Whether you marry my brother or not

14
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,160
depends on

15
00:01:05,361 --> 00:01:06,400
how well you behave.

16
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:21,361
Young Master Yan, we've arrived.

17
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,320
I don't want to get married.

18
00:01:25,801 --> 00:01:26,760
That's not an option.

19
00:01:27,481 --> 00:01:28,760
Miss Xia is waiting for you.

20
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,680
You know,

21
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,240
I don't want to marry her at all.

22
00:01:33,001 --> 00:01:33,801
I want to marry you.

23
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,561
Young Master Yan, no.

24
00:01:51,721 --> 00:01:52,561
Lord,

25
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:55,240
let us come before you

26
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,441
to witness together.

27
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,801
Bless this couple

28
00:01:57,801 --> 00:02:00,441
as they enter the sacred hall of marriage.

29
00:02:01,001 --> 00:02:02,320
Amen.

30
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,841
Bride,

31
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,361
do you take this man

32
00:02:06,361 --> 00:02:07,601
to be your husband

33
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,761
and enter into marriage with him?

34
00:02:10,801 --> 00:02:11,801
I do.

35
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,440
Groom,

36
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:15,081
do you take

37
00:02:15,081 --> 00:02:17,120
this woman to be your wife?

38
00:02:19,921 --> 00:02:21,520
I don't think he wants to.

39
00:02:24,801 --> 00:02:26,641
I'm abroad,

40
00:02:26,761 --> 00:02:29,921
but I know what's going on at home.

41
00:02:33,201 --> 00:02:34,440
Your marriage

42
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,560
ties two families together.

43
00:02:37,201 --> 00:02:39,680
I hope you both take it seriously.

44
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,321
Cheng Yan,

45
00:02:41,321 --> 00:02:42,761
the one you want to marry

46
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,520
isn't Xia Wanqing, is it?

47
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,481
So, are you going to

48
00:02:49,641 --> 00:02:51,481
marry her or not?

49
00:02:51,801 --> 00:02:52,960
It's up to you.

50
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,560
Are you marrying her?

51
00:03:08,321 --> 00:03:09,120
Young Master Yan,

52
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,761
just marry Miss Xia.

53
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,601
Who do you think you are?

54
00:03:21,321 --> 00:03:23,280
Why do you get to decide

55
00:03:23,801 --> 00:03:25,400
if he gets married?

56
00:03:26,161 --> 00:03:27,081
I...

57
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,801
Xia Wanqing,

58
00:03:29,801 --> 00:03:30,720
that's too much!

59
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,921
How could you hit someone?

60
00:03:32,081 --> 00:03:32,801
What are you doing?

61
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,801
Looks like

62
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:38,240
you want to marry her, huh?

63
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,440
I'm not

64
00:03:41,201 --> 00:03:42,440
getting married!

65
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,321
My daughter.

66
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,520
Xiaoxue,

67
00:03:50,161 --> 00:03:50,881
are you okay?

68
00:04:14,521 --> 00:04:15,240
I'm sorry.

69
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,640
Young Master Yan, please don't say that.

70
00:04:22,841 --> 00:04:24,161
I shouldn't have said anything.

71
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,601
No matter what,

72
00:04:31,361 --> 00:04:33,120
I won't let you get hurt again.

73
00:04:35,721 --> 00:04:37,521
Actually, I can understand Miss Xia.

74
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,481
If I were in her shoes,

75
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,801
I might not have been as calm as she was.

76
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,680
Besides,

77
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,000
I don't have any status.

78
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,640
Don't worry.

79
00:04:53,401 --> 00:04:54,481
I'll give you an explanation.

80
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:03,921
Chengyan.

81
00:05:14,161 --> 00:05:15,680
Xiaoxue, you're here too.

82
00:05:16,481 --> 00:05:17,080
Mr. Gu.

83
00:05:17,801 --> 00:05:18,760
You guys talk first.

84
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,721
I'll go first.

85
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,760
Wait.

86
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:23,680
Xiaoxue, I came this time

87
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,481
to talk to Chengyan

88
00:05:25,481 --> 00:05:26,760
with Chengyan about you.

89
00:05:28,841 --> 00:05:29,481
Chengyan,

90
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,161
as you can see,

91
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:34,361
Wanqing seems to have a big problem with Xiaoxue.

92
00:05:35,481 --> 00:05:37,200
I have a big problem with her too.

93
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,841
How could she beat me up?

94
00:05:39,521 --> 00:05:41,080
If it weren't for the Xia Family,

95
00:05:41,361 --> 00:05:41,680
I...

96
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,560
What I mean is,

97
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,760
we shouldn't put too much energy

98
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,801
into this matter.

99
00:05:46,161 --> 00:05:47,481
Now that your leg's healed,

100
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:51,320
if it's not working out, just let Xiaoxue go.

101
00:05:52,601 --> 00:05:54,000
She just beat up my people,

102
00:05:54,161 --> 00:05:55,240
and you want me to let her go?

103
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,440
If we get married,

104
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,560
will she be in charge then?

105
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,361
Ji Xiaoxue can't leave.

106
00:06:06,481 --> 00:06:08,000
Well, maybe I should...

107
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,161
Xiaoxue really can't leave.

108
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,120
I brought her here.

109
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,041
She hasn't done anything wrong

110
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:15,440
she hasn't done anything wrong.

111
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,041
I think she's innocent.

112
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,041
If you don't love Wanqing,

113
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,560
then don't

114
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,320
get married.

115
00:06:25,361 --> 00:06:26,080
Xiaoxue,

116
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:27,440
come with me.

117
00:06:30,841 --> 00:06:31,521
Chengyan,

118
00:06:36,041 --> 00:06:36,841
Xiaoxue

119
00:06:37,361 --> 00:06:38,401
can stay for now.

120
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:43,361
But you can't lose Wanqing.

121
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,521
Why did you say that to Wanqing in the church?

122
00:06:59,080 --> 00:06:59,801
Answer me!

123
00:07:02,841 --> 00:07:05,281
Only if Wanqing and Yan get married,

124
00:07:05,961 --> 00:07:07,560
can I be with you.

125
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,161
As long as you can be with me,

126
00:07:17,801 --> 00:07:19,080
will you do anything?

127
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,041
Yes,

128
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,440
I will do anything.

129
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,921
Mr. Gu, are you looking for me?

130
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,841
Xiaoxue, sit.

131
00:08:02,961 --> 00:08:03,961
I already know

132
00:08:04,481 --> 00:08:05,560
something.

133
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,240
Mr. Gu,

134
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:12,161
did I do something wrong?

135
00:08:12,481 --> 00:08:13,721
I'm not trying to blame you.

136
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,281
I just want to tell you

137
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,841
that you and Cheng Yan are impossible.

138
00:08:20,601 --> 00:08:22,560
Mr. Gu, do you think

139
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,961
I'm too close to Yan?

140
00:08:25,841 --> 00:08:26,640
Don't worry.

141
00:08:27,041 --> 00:08:29,041
I know my place.

142
00:08:29,881 --> 00:08:31,680
I won't be a fool.

143
00:08:31,921 --> 00:08:34,360
It has nothing to do with status.

144
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,680
I told you.

145
00:08:36,881 --> 00:08:38,041
If you need money,

146
00:08:38,401 --> 00:08:40,161
you can use the card I gave you.

147
00:08:40,521 --> 00:08:42,720
But you and Chengyan

148
00:08:43,161 --> 00:08:44,801
can't be together.

149
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,241
I never thought about

150
00:08:49,241 --> 00:08:50,641
being with him.

151
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,001
But

152
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,720
why are you so nice to me?

153
00:08:57,641 --> 00:08:59,041
I've told you before,

154
00:08:59,121 --> 00:09:00,440
don't think too much

155
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,560
or ask too many questions.

156
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,641
It's not good for us

157
00:09:02,641 --> 00:09:04,200
to think too much or ask too many questions.

158
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,080
You should think about

159
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,440
your future now.
